  \begin {tikzcd}
    E^C\ar [rr, bend left, "F^*"] & \bot  & E^D\ar [ll, bend left, "G^*"]\makebox [0pt][l].
  \end {tikzcd}

We demonstrate the triangle identities in components. The left
  triangle identity asserts that 




